[
    {
        "text": "This is a checkup for subjective pronouns\nand ‘be’ verbs.",
        "start": 0.079,
        "duration": 5.05
    },
    {
        "text": "Let’s take a look at the board.",
        "start": 5.129,
        "duration": 2.413
    },
    {
        "text": "The first sentence.",
        "start": 7.542,
        "duration": 1.767
    },
    {
        "text": "“___, are bags.”",
        "start": 9.309,
        "duration": 2.837
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, bags are things.",
        "start": 12.146,
        "duration": 2.693
    },
    {
        "text": "So we can’t say “he” or “she” or,\nyou know, any of those.",
        "start": 14.839,
        "duration": 4.201
    },
    {
        "text": "We have to use “it” or “they”.",
        "start": 19.04,
        "duration": 3.35
