        "duration": 0.713
    },
    {
        "text": "“Yes, they are.”",
        "start": 105.252,
        "duration": 1.741
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, let’s move on to the next part.",
        "start": 106.993,
        "duration": 3.142
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, now we’re going to focus on negatives\nand questions.",
        "start": 110.135,
        "duration": 4.656
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, the first sentence says,",
        "start": 114.791,
        "duration": 2.433
    },
    {
        "text": "“I’m a student”.",
