    },
    {
        "text": "Right…",
        "start": 127.612,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Remember, ‘not’ goes after the ‘be’\nverb.",
        "start": 128.612,
        "duration": 2.971
    },
    {
        "text": "“I am…am not.”",
        "start": 131.583,
        "duration": 4.556
    },
    {
        "text": "And then the noun.\n“…a student.”",
        "start": 136.139,
        "duration": 2.912
    },
    {
        "text": "“I’m not a student.”",
        "start": 139.051,
        "duration": 2.854
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 141.905,
        "duration": 0.872
    },
    {
        "text": "“They are teachers.”",
        "start": 142.777,
        "duration": 2.556
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 145.333,
        "duration": 1.397
    },
    {
        "text": "And now we have some other people...",
        "start": 146.73,
        "duration": 2.296
    },
    {
        "text": "and that’s not true.",
        "start": 149.026,
        "duration": 2.303
    },
    {
