    },
    {
        "text": "“No, I’m not”.",
        "start": 195.992,
        "duration": 2.008
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, let’s move on to the last part.",
        "start": 198.0,
        "duration": 3.59
    },
    {
        "text": "Now for this last part, we’re going to look\nat some sentences,",
        "start": 201.59,
