    {
        "text": " but there’s something wrong in all of these sentences.",
        "start": 205.9,
        "duration": 3.831
    },
    {
        "text": "So you have to find the mistakes.",
        "start": 209.731,
        "duration": 3.579
    },
    {
        "text": "The first sentence says, “I’m student”.",
        "start": 213.31,
        "duration": 5.516
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, look, “student”.",
        "start": 218.826,
        "duration": 2.422
    },
    {
        "text": "There’s no ‘s’.",
        "start": 221.248,
        "duration": 1.759
    },
    {
        "text": "That means just one.",
